/**
 * Saves the cursor position and prepares for calls to functions 
 * <b>filter_get_string</b>, <b>filter_put_string</b>, and 
 * <b>filter_restore_pos</b>.
 * 
 * @see filter_get_string
 * @see filter_put_string
